rows.label: tlk42100151_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The kid from the fish shop often
gives me food. I hear their mother
is very ill, which must be hard.

rows.label: tlk42100151_04_msg0002
rows.name:
That kid's cooking is so
gentle, it reminds me of Gula.

rows.label: tlk42100151_04_msg0003
rows.name:
You should give them your
business if you can. It would
help their mother, after all.
